  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "[---]\r\n中國的飲食文化淵遠流長，舉世皆知。現今，雖然在國際上各大都市均可吃到中國菜，在台灣也能品嚐到各式各樣的中國菜餚，尤其是各大夜市的美食琳瑯滿目，物超所值。",
      "ab": "saringan rali’, ana alang inu’ ba’ ci tatahuk raramat na Taluw kora’. ana maki’ ana inu’ tehkan mani’ ka raramat na Taluw. ga, kumaṟal ka ci’uli’ paṟigaw ga, nanak Taywan ka lanlamu’ na raramat Taluw cel masasli’ ki’ ma. umabas ka pasasli’ maginbiniy ci nani’un malahngan. mahyuw ci masinpayux ka raramat.",
